      <title>Mango Markets 是最新一个与美国证券交易委员会达成和解的加密货币项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/mango-markets-is-latest-crypto-project-to-settle-sec-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[运营陷入困境的去中心化金融项目 Mango Markets 的实体已就出售未注册证券和充当经纪人向美国证券交易委员会提出的指控达成和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/mango-markets-is-latest-crypto-project-to-settle-sec-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:42:34 GMT</pubDate>
