    <item>
      <title>国际劳工组织秘书长洪博希望企业避免港口罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/ilo-s-houngbo-hopes-companies-avoid-port-strikes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际劳工组织总干事吉尔伯特·洪博讨论了 10 月 1 日美国东海岸和墨西哥湾沿岸港口罢工的可能性。洪博在接受“彭博市场”采访时表示：“这多少让你了解了工人们可能陷入的痛苦境地。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/ilo-s-houngbo-hopes-companies-avoid-port-strikes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Petrofac 债权人同意将大部分债务转换为股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/petrofac-creditors-agree-to-convert-majority-of-debt-into-equity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据周五的一份声明称，Petrofac Ltd 已与一些主要利益相关者达成初步协议，债权人将把公司的大部分债务转换为股权，从而大幅稀释现有股东的股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/petrofac-creditors-agree-to-convert-majority-of-debt-into-equity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥重要财政官员将在过渡期间离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/key-mexican-finance-official-to-leave-in-presidential-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥财政部级别第二高、任期最长的高级官员即将离职，这在总统过渡期间是一个令人惊讶的进展，因为官员们一直向投资者强调总统过渡的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/key-mexican-finance-official-to-leave-in-presidential-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:07:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>糖业巨头 Cosan 考虑出售淡水河谷股份以应对杠杆问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/sugar-giant-cosan-mulls-selling-vale-stake-on-leverage-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁鲁本斯·奥梅托 (Rubens Ometto) 的企业集团 Cosan SA 正在考虑出售包括其在矿业巨头淡水河谷 (Vale SA) 持有的价值 22 亿美元的股份在内的资产，此举可能会解除一笔失败的赌注以偿还债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/sugar-giant-cosan-mulls-selling-vale-stake-on-leverage-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:56:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度放宽大米出口限制，为全球消费者提供缓冲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/india-eases-curbs-on-rice-exports-cushioning-global-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度放松了部分大米出口限制，此举可能缓解全球大米价格，并预示着最近全国大选后国内农业政策将发生转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/india-eases-curbs-on-rice-exports-cushioning-global-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:02:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车因汽车需求减弱再次下调利润预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/volkswagen-lowers-forecast-again-on-waning-car-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团今年第二次下调了业绩预期，警告称，在该公司与工会就可能的裁员和史无前例的工厂关闭问题展开斗争之际，需求减弱将削弱这家德国汽车制造商的盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/volkswagen-lowers-forecast-again-on-waning-car-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 16:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
